
<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile_image.jpg", width: 150, height: 150, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">

        <p>A web developer, with a strong background in software application support. I have a deep knowledge in configuring software applications to suit company needs. Robotics is my passion and I am currently working on at home alarm system. </p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Jefferies LLC (2011-2014) - Audio Visual Technician
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Stonemor LP (2014-2017) - Tier 2 Software Application Support
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              NYCDA - Web Development Bootcamp (Specializing in Full-Stack Development )
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Kingsborough Community College (2009-2011)
            </div>

          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
